1. *Beži* iz sobe! (Run out of the room!)
2. On je *bežao* od policije. (He was running away from the police.)
3. Ona je *bežala* preko polja. (She was running across the field.) 
4. Oni su *bežali* od tuče. (They were running away from the fight.)
5. Oni su *bežali* svojim životima. (They were running for their lives.)